  "description": "COORD-7 gate: P2 (Orks, AI at Hard) plays a live Shooting phase. Asserts (a) the army-wide 'Shooting plan' card (FOCUS allocations with expected damage vs HP, soften-only charge targets, free-fire units) reaches GameEventLog as its own card, and (b) the plan is honest — executed 'shoots at' combat headers from shooters listed in the plan hit only their announced targets (GameEventLog.shooting_plan_integrity() reports zero mismatches), with replans narrated as new cards rather than silent greedy fallback. Screenshots capture the log panel with the plan card visible.",
  "steps": [
    {
